      "x": 1005,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 234,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "Same direction (overtaking):\n  Relative = S1 - S2\n  ──→  ──→\n\nOpposite direction (crossing):\n  Relative = S1 + S2\n  ──→  ←──",
