    {
      "id": "el_25",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 657,
      "width": 332,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Train must cover own length + platform\n  D = 200+300 = 500m in 25s\nStep 2: S = 500/25 = 20 m/s = 20×18/5 = 72\n\nTRICK:\nTrain→Platform: D = L+P always\nS = (L+P)/T\n\n  ┌────────────┐ ╠════════════╣\n  │Train (200m) │→ Platform(300m)\n  └────────────┘ ╠════════════╣\n  |◄──────── 500m ──────────►|\n\nAnswer: 72 km/h ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 25,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Train must cover own length + platform\n  D = 200+300 = 500m in 25s\nStep 2: S = 500/25 = 20 m/s = 20×18/5 = 72\n\nTRICK:\nTrain→Platform: D = L+P always\nS = (L+P)/T\n\n  ┌────────────┐ ╠════════════╣\n  │Train (200m) │→ Platform(300m)\n  └────────────┘ ╠════════════╣\n  |◄──────── 500m ──────────►|\n\nAnswer: 72 km/h ✓",
