    {
      "id": "el_30",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 657,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: S = 72×5/18 = 20 m/s\nStep 2: L = S×T = 20×10 = 200m\n\nTRICK:\nL = S(m/s) × T(sec)\nConvert km/h first: ×5/18\n\n  ┌──────── ? m ────────┐\n  │      Train          │───→ 72 km/h\n  └─────────────────────┘\n              | pole\n\n72×5/18=20 m/s, L=20×10=200m\n\nAnswer: 200m ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
