      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: S = 72×5/18 = 20 m/s\nStep 2: L = S×T = 20×10 = 200m\n\nTRICK:\nL = S(m/s) × T(sec)\nConvert km/h first: ×5/18\n\n  ┌──────── ? m ────────┐\n  │      Train          │───→ 72 km/h\n  └─────────────────────┘\n              | pole\n\n72×5/18=20 m/s, L=20×10=200m\n\nAnswer: 200m ✓",
