    {
      "id": "el_35",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1054,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: S=90×5/18=25 m/s\n  Total dist covered = 25×30 = 750m\nStep 2: Platform = Total-Train = 750-250\n\nTRICK:\nP = S×T - L = 25×30 - 250 = 500m\n\n  ┌────────────┐ ╠═══ ? m ═══╣\n  │Train (250m) │→ Platform(?)\n  └────────────┘ ╠══════════╣\n\nAnswer: 500m ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
