    {
      "id": "el_40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1054,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D = Train+Bridge = 300+200 = 500m\n  S = 54×5/18 = 15 m/s\nStep 2: T = D/S = 500/15 = 33.33 sec\n\nTRICK:\nT = (L+P)/S = (300+200)/(54×5/18)\n= 500/15 = 33.33s\n\n  ┌────────────┐ ╠════════════╣\n  │Train (300m) │→ Bridge(200m)\n  └────────────┘ ╠════════════╣\n\nAnswer: 33.33 sec ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
