      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D = Train+Bridge = 300+200 = 500m\n  S = 54×5/18 = 15 m/s\nStep 2: T = D/S = 500/15 = 33.33 sec\n\nTRICK:\nT = (L+P)/S = (300+200)/(54×5/18)\n= 500/15 = 33.33s\n\n  ┌────────────┐ ╠════════════╣\n  │Train (300m) │→ Bridge(200m)\n  └────────────┘ ╠════════════╣\n\nAnswer: 33.33 sec ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
