      "y": 1070,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Opposite→Rel=40+32=72 km/h=20 m/s\n  D = L1+L2 = 150+200 = 350m\nStep 2: T = 350/20 = 17.5 sec\n\nTRICK:\nT = (L1+L2)/(S1+S2) in m/s\n= 350/20 = 17.5s\n\n  ┌──────────┐         ┌───────────┐\n  │T1 (150m) │──→  ←──│ T2 (200m) │\n  └──────────┘ 40  32  └───────────┘\n\nAnswer: 17.5 sec ✓",
