      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1373,
      "width": 801,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "Two trains 100 meters and 150 meters long are running at\n60 km/h and 40 km/h in the same direction. How long will\nthe faster train take to overtake the slower one?",
      "fontSize": 13,
