    {
      "id": "el_50",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1454,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Same dir→Rel=60-40=20 km/h=50/9 m/s\n  D = L1+L2 = 100+150 = 250m\nStep 2: T = 250/(50/9) = 250×9/50 = 45s\n\nTRICK:\nT = (L1+L2)/(S1-S2) in m/s\n= 250/(50/9) = 45s\n\n  ┌──────────┐  ┌───────────┐\n  │T1 (100m) │→ │ T2 (150m) │→\n  └──────────┘60 └───────────┘40\n\nAnswer: 45 sec ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5000,
