      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Same dir→Rel=60-40=20 km/h=50/9 m/s\n  D = L1+L2 = 100+150 = 250m\nStep 2: T = 250/(50/9) = 250×9/50 = 45s\n\nTRICK:\nT = (L1+L2)/(S1-S2) in m/s\n= 250/(50/9) = 45s\n\n  ┌──────────┐  ┌───────────┐\n  │T1 (100m) │→ │ T2 (150m) │→\n  └──────────┘60 └───────────┘40\n\nAnswer: 45 sec ✓",
