      "x": 535,
      "y": 1454,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Same dir → Rel=60-6=54 km/h=15 m/s\n  Person=point → D=200m only\nStep 2: T = 200/15 = 13.33 sec\n\nTRICK:\nPerson has NO length → D=train L only\nT = L/(S_train-S_man) in m/s\n\n  ┌──────────────┐     🚶\n  │ Train (200m)  │──→  ──→\n  └──────────────┘ 60    6\n\n= 200/15 = 13.33s\n\nAnswer: 13.33 sec ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
