      "width": 296,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Opposite→Rel=72+18=90 km/h=25 m/s\n  D=180m (person=point)\nStep 2: T = 180/25 = 7.2 sec\n\nTRICK:\nT = L/(S_train+S_man) in m/s\n= 180/(90×5/18) = 180/25 = 7.2s\n\n  ┌──────────────┐   🚶\n  │ Train (180m)  │─→ ←─\n  └──────────────┘ 72  18\n\nAnswer: 7.2 sec ✓",
