    {
      "id": "el_65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1883,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D=120+180=300m, T=12s\n  Rel = 300/12 = 25 m/s = 90 km/h\nStep 2: Opposite: S1+S2=90 → S2=90-50=40\n\nTRICK:\nRel = (L1+L2)/T → convert to km/h\nThen: S2 = Rel-S1 (opposite dir)\n\n  ──→ (120m)    (180m) ←──\n   50 km/h       ? km/h\n\n25 m/s×18/5=90 → S2=90-50=40\n\nAnswer: S2 = 40 km/h ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
