    {
      "id": "el_75",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1867,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Pole: L=S×12. Platform: L+240=S×24\n  Subtract: 240=S×12 → S=20 m/s\nStep 2: L=20×12=240m. S=20×18/5=72 km/h\n\nTRICK (subtract scenarios):\nExtra dist=240m, Extra time=24-12=12s\nS = 240/12 = 20 m/s\nL = S×T_pole = 20×12 = 240m\n\nPole:12s → L=S×12\nPlatform:24s → L+P=S×24\nSubtract → P=S×12\n\nAnswer: L=240m, S=72 km/h ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 75,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_12"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Pole: L=S×12. Platform: L+240=S×24\n  Subtract: 240=S×12 → S=20 m/s\nStep 2: L=20×12=240m. S=20×18/5=72 km/h\n\nTRICK (subtract scenarios):\nExtra dist=240m, Extra time=24-12=12s\nS = 240/12 = 20 m/s\nL = S×T_pole = 20×12 = 240m\n\nPole:12s → L=S×12\nPlatform:24s → L+P=S×24\nSubtract → P=S×12\n\nAnswer: L=240m, S=72 km/h ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
