    {
      "id": "el_80",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2281,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Man at END of bridge\n  Train nose must travel 200m to reach him\nStep 2: S=36×5/18=10 m/s, T=200/10=20s\n\nTRICK:\nKEY: man's position matters!\nD = distance to the man, NOT L+bridge\n\n           ╠══ 200m ══╣\n  ┌──────┐ ║  Bridge  ║🚶\n  │Train  │→╠═════════╣\n   10 m/s\n\nT = 200/10 = 20 sec\n\nAnswer: 20 sec ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
