        "type_13"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Man at END of bridge\n  Train nose must travel 200m to reach him\nStep 2: S=36×5/18=10 m/s, T=200/10=20s\n\nTRICK:\nKEY: man's position matters!\nD = distance to the man, NOT L+bridge\n\n           ╠══ 200m ══╣\n  ┌──────┐ ║  Bridge  ║🚶\n  │Train  │→╠═════════╣\n   10 m/s\n\nT = 200/10 = 20 sec\n\nAnswer: 20 sec ✓",
