      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2281,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: S=108×5/18=30 m/s\n  Inside: rear enters→nose exits=T-L\n  Exit: nose enters→rear exits=T+L\nStep 2: Inside=2000-500=1500→1500/30=50s\n  Exit=2000+500=2500→2500/30=83.3s\n\nTRICK:\nInside (hidden): D=Tunnel-Train=T-L\nThrough (exit): D=Tunnel+Train=T+L\n\n  ████ Tunnel 2000m ████\n   ┌──500m──┐\n\nInside=1500/30=50s, Exit=2500/30=83.3s\n\nAnswer: Inside=50s, Exit=83.3s ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
