      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2200,
      "width": 787,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "Two trains start from stations A and B, 450 km apart,\nheading towards each other at 60 km/h and 90 km/h. When\nand where will they meet?",
