    {
      "id": "el_90",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2281,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Opposite→Rel=60+90=150 km/h\n  T=450/150=3 hrs. From A: 60×3=180km\n\nTRICK (ratio shortcut):\nSpeed ratio=60:90=2:3\nFrom A = (2/5)×450 = 180 km\nNo need to find time!\n\n  A ────── 450 km ────── B\n  ──→ 60            90 ←──\n       meet 180km from A\n\nAnswer: Meet in 3 hrs, 180km from A ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 9000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 90,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_15"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Opposite→Rel=60+90=150 km/h\n  T=450/150=3 hrs. From A: 60×3=180km\n\nTRICK (ratio shortcut):\nSpeed ratio=60:90=2:3\nFrom A = (2/5)×450 = 180 km\nNo need to find time!\n\n  A ────── 450 km ────── B\n  ──→ 60            90 ←──\n       meet 180km from A\n\nAnswer: Meet in 3 hrs, 180km from A ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
