      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2627,
      "width": 816,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A train crosses a pole in 20 seconds at 54 km/h. How long\nwill it take to cross the pole if the speed is increased\nto 72 km/h?",
      "fontSize": 13,
