    {
      "id": "el_95",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2708,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: L=S×T→same L, so S1×T1=S2×T2\n  54×20 = 72×T2 → T2 = 1080/72 = 15s\n\nTRICK (inverse ratio):\nSame dist → Speed:Time are INVERSE\nS=54:72=3:4 → T=4:3\nNew T = 20×(3/4) = 15 sec\n\nSpeed ↑ → Time ↓ (always inverse!)\n\nAnswer: 15 sec ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 9500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 95,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_16"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: L=S×T→same L, so S1×T1=S2×T2\n  54×20 = 72×T2 → T2 = 1080/72 = 15s\n\nTRICK (inverse ratio):\nSame dist → Speed:Time are INVERSE\nS=54:72=3:4 → T=4:3\nNew T = 20×(3/4) = 15 sec\n\nSpeed ↑ → Time ↓ (always inverse!)\n\nAnswer: 15 sec ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
