    {
      "id": "el_105",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2724,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Train crosses MAN (not train!)\n  Man=point → D=150m only (NOT 150+100!)\nStep 2: Rel=150/10=15 m/s=54 km/h\n  Same dir: S1-36=54 → S1=90\n\nTRICK (TRAP alert!):\nCrosses man IN another train:\nD=crossing train's length ONLY\nNOT sum of both trains!\n\n  ┌──────────┐  ┌─────────┐\n  │T1 (150m) │→ │T2 🚶100m│→\n  └──────────┘S1 └─────────┘36\n\nAnswer: S1 = 90 km/h ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
