      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 3056,
      "width": 816,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "Two trains of equal length cross a pole in 20 seconds and\n30 seconds respectively. How long will they take to cross\neach other when running in opposite directions?",
