    {
      "id": "el_110",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 3137,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: L=S1×20=S2×30. D=2L\n  Opp: T=2L/(S1+S2)=2L/(L/20+L/30)\n  =2/(1/20+1/30)=2/(50/600)=2400/50=24s\n\nTRICK (equal length formula):\nOpp: 2×T1×T2/(T1+T2) = 2×20×30/50 = 24s\nSame: 2×T1×T2/(T1-T2) = 1200/10 = 120s\n\n  ──→ A (L)      (L) ←──\n  pole:20s     pole:30s\n\nAnswer: Opp=24s, Same=120s ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 11000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 110,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_19"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: L=S1×20=S2×30. D=2L\n  Opp: T=2L/(S1+S2)=2L/(L/20+L/30)\n  =2/(1/20+1/30)=2/(50/600)=2400/50=24s\n\nTRICK (equal length formula):\nOpp: 2×T1×T2/(T1+T2) = 2×20×30/50 = 24s\nSame: 2×T1×T2/(T1-T2) = 1200/10 = 120s\n\n  ──→ A (L)      (L) ←──\n  pole:20s     pole:30s\n\nAnswer: Opp=24s, Same=120s ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
